text: Symeon of Polotsk was born in the year 1768, and was a member of the Royal House, the highest of the French nobility. The Royal House of Polotsk was the family that had ruled the French kingdom for over 200 years. It had been ruled by a series of kings, and was known for being extremely secretive.
